---
title: Tex-Mex Beef and Rice Skillet with Cheddar Cheese and Lime Crema
description: This colourful, no-fuss Tex-Mex skillet is packed with flavour thanks to spiced rice and salsa-coated beef and peppers. Melty cheese and a dollop of lime crema is all you need to make your tastebuds sing!
